        <updateDate>2021-09-15T21:14:11Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Saving Hypodermic Injections and Offering vaccines to Taxpayers Swiftly Act of 2021 or the SHOTS Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill prohibits any alien who is not a lawful permanent resident from receiving a COVID-19 vaccine until the earlier of (1) the date when all U.S. nationals and lawful permanent residents who wish to receive a vaccine have been fully vaccinated, or (2) December 31, 2021. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
